        "TileImage": "$($repository 1e7b2e92-13f0-4dea-b656-f86f0896f362).Image",
        "Description": "Good evening 47. \rAfter your recent  performance in ICA Training, we have determined our current mission&apos;s chances of success to be higher in the hands of a more &quot;youthful&quot; Agent. \rThe operation was planned to have already taken place, however a recent spike in network activity leads us to believe security has gotten wind of our mission.\r\rYour job will be to take out key security personnel on Agent 67&apos;s planned route. They will engage shortly after you, so try to remain silent.\rGood luck 47.",
